{"tid":783591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"堅信人性本善！情侶騎單車遊「ISIS恐怖領地」慘遭輾斃","createTime":"2018-08-17T15:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T04:44:49.000Z","uid":82829,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"41ac653e676636ba6c62dead44819aec75fe3395","tid":783591,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201808/cc77fab9801dcca6e9d2b76f6a104101.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201808%2Fcc77fab9801dcca6e9d2b76f6a104101.JPG&h=87614102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你相信人性本善嗎？美國一對年輕情侶為了到各地壯遊，放棄高薪好工作，2人日前抱持著人性本善的理念，大膽前進才剛慘遭伊斯蘭國（ISIS）攻擊的塔吉克斯坦共和國，沒想到卻仍逃不出恐怖攻擊，2人最後都遭到輾斃慘死異鄉，而ISIS國隨後也公布2人遇害的影片，殘忍誓言要殺死「不信者」。<br />\n▼（圖／Dailymail／<a href=\"http://simplycycling.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsimplycycling.org&d=HznOOnqaT1YeGSJD2gOPpYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a6f79f36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">simplycycling.org</a>）<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201808/9247d88f60d29c360b2b08b78ff2260a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201808%2F9247d88f60d29c360b2b08b78ff2260a.JPG&h=6bc04f88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201808/a0f5602cc0be88b7b4a83b4ca7de36a9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201808%2Fa0f5602cc0be88b7b4a83b4ca7de36a9.JPG&h=b1dae234&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綜合外媒報導，來自美國的杰伊和羅蘭（Jay Austin and Lauren Geoghegan）2人預計從非洲騎單車，開始一連串的壯遊之旅前，還特別創立了一個網站「Simply Cycling」，分享了許多在旅途中遇到的一切美好事物。諷刺的是，杰伊在進入塔吉克斯坦共和國之前，還自信滿滿地在網站上寫下，「從新聞上看，你會覺得這個世界很可怕，那些文章說人類不值得信任、糟糕、邪惡，但我不相信。邪惡是我們發明出的概念，是虛構的。總體來說，人類是善良的。人有時自私，有時短視，但人依然是慷慨、美好、善良的」。<br />\n▼（圖／Dailymail／<a href=\"http://simplycycling.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsimplycycling.org&d=HznOOnqaT1YeGSJD2gOPpYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a6f79f36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">simplycycling.org</a>）<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201808/80dceb076ed4665bdcece5e1c4a0be23.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201808%2F80dceb076ed4665bdcece5e1c4a0be23.JPG&h=1db0ab0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201808/1599c0d7be2a4291d04dc193229d2367.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201808%2F1599c0d7be2a4291d04dc193229d2367.JPG&h=2170c68a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n豈料，他們兩人與其他旅行者騎著單車在塔吉克斯坦的公路上，沒多久竟被一輛轎車狂追不捨，追上後還故意迴轉「正面輾過他們一群人」，導致所有人當場喪命。<br />\n▼（圖／Youtube／Ozodivideo）<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201808/eb2793c1ee724865a6f2f8a2353bb964.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201808%2Feb2793c1ee724865a6f2f8a2353bb964.JPG&h=f79f9c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不只如此，ISIS事後還將這群人的死亡影片發布到網路上，只見轎車上的5名襲擊者也都出現在鏡頭前，慘不忍睹的駭人畫面，令人看了不勝唏噓。<br />\n（封面圖／Dailymail／<a href=\"http://simplycycling.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsimplycycling.org&d=HznOOnqaT1YeGSJD2gOPpYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a6f79f36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">simplycycling.org</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/堅信人性本善-情侶騎單車遊-isis恐怖領地-慘遭輾斃-064000850.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%A0%85%E4%BF%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%80%A7%E6%9C%AC%E5%96%84-%E6%83%85%E4%BE%B6%E9%A8%8E%E5%96%AE%E8%BB%8A%E9%81%8A-isis%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E9%A0%98%E5%9C%B0-%E6%85%98%E9%81%AD%E8%BC%BE%E6%96%83-064000850.html&d=HznOOnqaT1YeGSJD2gOPpYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=8f1edea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/堅信人性本善-情侶騎單車遊-isis恐怖領地-慘遭輾斃-064000850.html</a>"},{"pid":"94bce019773126dcae3fd54c0b73e7ea0e13a940","tid":783591,"uid":32765,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"htt